<p>RPM Automotive leverages the latest in automotive technology including state of the art equipment and the most highly trained automotive mechanics in the industry</p>
<p>
<table border="0">
<tbody>
<tr>
<td><a href="http://www.myjaxchamber.com/" target="_black"> <img style="height: 50px;" src="/image.axd?picture=2013%2f5%2fWEBSITE_USE_MEMBER_LOGO_LARGE.JPG" border="0" alt="Jax Chamber Member" /></a></td>
<td><a href="http://www.facebook.com/rpmautomotive"><img style="border-style: initial; border-color: initial;" src="/image.axd?picture=2012%2f1%2ffacebook_40x40.jpg" alt="" /></a></td>
<td><a href="http://www.youtube.com/rpmautomotivejaxfl"><img style="border-style: initial; border-color: initial;" src="/image.axd?picture=2012%2f1%2fyoutube.jpg" alt="" /></a></td>
<td><a href="http://aaa.com"><img style="border-style: initial; border-color: initial;" src="/image.axd?picture=2012%2f2%2fAAA.JPG" alt="" height="50" /></a></td>
<td><a href="/page/calendar.aspx"> 
<table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
<tbody>
<tr>
<td><img src="/image.axd?picture=2012%2f9%2fcalendar40.gif" alt="" /></td>

</tbody>
</table>
</a></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</p>
<p><img src="/image.axd?picture=2009%2f12%2fTitleConvenientLocations.JPG" alt="" /></p>
<p>We have <a title="RPM Automotive has 8 convenient locations in the Jacksonville Jax area" href="/page/locations.aspx">eight convenient locations throughout the Jacksonville area</a>.&nbsp; You can find us in the following local areas:</p>
<ul>
<li><a href="/page/River-City.aspx">River City</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;</li>
</ul>
<ul>
<li><a href="/page/Avenues.aspx">The Avenues</a></li>
<li><a href="/page/Beaches.aspx">The Beaches</a></li>
<li><a href="/page/Fleming-Island.aspx">Fleming Island</a></li>
<li><a href="/page/Julington-Creek.aspx">Julington Creek</a></li>
<li><a href="/page/Ortega.aspx">Ortega</a></li>
<li><a href="/page/San-Marco.aspx">San Marco</a></li>
<li><a href="/page/Atlantic-at-San-Pablo.aspx">Atlantic at San Pablo</a></li>
</ul>
<p><img src="/image.axd?picture=2009%2f12%2fTitleWeCareAboutJacksonville.JPG" alt="" /></p>
<p>RPM Automotive is proud to be the primary corporate sponsor for Wolfson Children's Hospital in Jacksonville.&nbsp; Through the holidays RPM Automotive and Wolfson will be lighting candles to support children in their moment of the greatest need.&nbsp; This charitable work is only one example of how RPM Automotive participates in our community to give back to the city that we serve.</p>
<p>For more information about the Light a Candle charitable project please visit <a rel="NOFOLLOW" href="http://www.Wolfson55.org" target="_blank">www.Wolfson55.org</a>.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<div><br /></div>
